among our young.

1006
01:10:38.125 --> 01:10:39.958
-It's bullshit.
-It's not true.

1007
01:10:40.042 --> 01:10:41.208
She says he will only

1008
01:10:41.292 --> 01:10:42.958
bring more death.

1009
01:10:43.500 --> 01:10:44.500
Hey. why don't you

1010
01:10:44.583 --> 01:10:45.708
say something?

1011
01:10:46.583 --> 01:10:48.125
Just say something.
Please.

1012
01:10:54.125 --> 01:10:56.292
She says the outcast

1013
01:10:56.375 --> 01:10:57.583
may not stay in

1014
01:10:57.667 --> 01:10:58.500
