1070
01:12:49.917 --> 01:12:50.958
if you hadn't
disobeyed orders.

1071
01:12:51.042 --> 01:12:52.333
then your brother
would still be...

1072
01:12:59.583 --> 01:13:01.250
That wasn't my fault.

1073
01:13:01.333 --> 01:13:02.333
Dad. that...

1074
01:13:04.625 --> 01:13:05.333
That's not

1075
01:13:05.417 --> 01:13:06.417
