another son.

1079
01:13:39.875 --> 01:13:41.583
I've got nothing
to say to him.

1080
01:13:44.167 --> 01:13:45.542
Do not blame Lo'ak.

1081
01:13:48.625 --> 01:13:50.750
You said you could
protect this family.

1082
01:13:50.833 --> 01:13:52.083
That.
you could do.

1083
01:13:53.417 --> 01:13:55.125
Yeah. I thought
we would be safe here.

1084
01:13:55.208 --> 01:13:57.375
Our son is dead. Jake.

1085
01:13:58.125 --> 01:13:59.375
I was wrong!

1086
01:14:01.542 --> 01:14:02.625
What do you
want me to say?

1087
01:14:02.708 --> 01:14:03.833
That every decision
that I made

1088
01:14:03.917 --> 01:14:05.125
for this family is wrong?

1089
01:14:06.167 --> 01:14:07.500
I killed our son?

1090
01:14:13.000 --> 01:14:15.167
And still we are here
in this place.

1091
01:14:16.000 --> 01:14:17.833
hiding this pink skin.

1092
01:14:19.375 --> 01:14:20.375
this alien.

1093
01:14:20.458 --> 01:14:21.667
If I had to choose

1094
01:14:21.750 --> 01:14:24.083
between my family
